    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."AssignedVehicleId", a."AuthenticationSource", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."CreationTime", a."CreatorUserId", a."DeleterUserId", a."DeletionTime", a."DriverId", a."DriverName", a."EmailAddress", a."EmailConfirmationCode", a."IsActive", a."IsDeleted", a."IsEmailConfirmed", a."IsLockoutEnabled", a."IsPhoneNumberConfirmed", a."IsTwoFactorEnabled", a."LastModificationTime", a."LastModifierUserId", a."LockoutEndDateUtc", a."MechanicId", a."MechanicName", a."MunicipalityId", a."MunicipalityName", a."Name", a."NormalizedEmailAddress", a."NormalizedUserName", a."Password", a."PasswordResetCode", a."PhoneNumber", a."SecurityStamp", a."SupervisorId", a."SupervisorName", a."Surname", a."TenantId", a."UserName"
    FROM "AbpUsers" AS a
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (a."IsDeleted")) AND (@__ef_filter__p_2 OR a."TenantId" IS NULL)
    ORDER BY a."UserName"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS a1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."CreationTime", a0."CreatorUserId", a0."RoleId", a0."TenantId", a0."UserId"
    FROM "AbpUserRoles" AS a0
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_2 OR a0."TenantId" IS NULL
) AS a2 ON a1."Id" = a2."UserId"
ORDER BY a1."UserName", a1."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."AssignedVehicleId", a."AuthenticationSource", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."CreationTime", a."CreatorUserId", a."DeleterUserId", a."DeletionTime", a."DriverId", a."DriverName", a."EmailAddress", a."EmailConfirmationCode", a."IsActive", a."IsDeleted", a."IsEmailConfirmed", a."IsLockoutEnabled", a."IsPhoneNumberConfirmed", a."IsTwoFactorEnabled", a."LastModificationTime", a."LastModifierUserId", a."LockoutEndDateUtc", a."MechanicId", a."MechanicName", a."MunicipalityId", a."MunicipalityName", a."Name", a."NormalizedEmailAddress", a."NormalizedUserName", a."Password", a."PasswordResetCode", a."PhoneNumber", a."SecurityStamp", a."SupervisorId", a."SupervisorName", a."Surname", a."TenantId", a."UserName"
    FROM "AbpUsers" AS a
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (a."IsDeleted")) AND (@__ef_filter__p_2 OR a."TenantId" IS NULL)
    ORDER BY a."UserName"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS a1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."CreationTime", a0."CreatorUserId", a0."RoleId", a0."TenantId", a0."UserId"
    FROM "AbpUserRoles" AS a0
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_2 OR a0."TenantId" IS NULL
) AS a2 ON a1."Id" = a2."UserId"
ORDER BY a1."UserName", a1."Id"
